/https://www.cnn.com/2020/04/09/us/home-from-home-charity-livestream-trnd/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

为向WHO捐赠善款，其他一些名人围绕着疫情创立衣服生产线，像[[哈利·斯泰爾斯|哈利]]风格体恤运动<ref>{{Cite web|title=Harry Styles' Charity Shirt: Details|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9352960/harry-styles-charity-shirt|date=2020-04-07|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|website=Billboard|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423090247/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9352960/harry-styles-charity-shirt|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[萊恩·雷諾斯|瑞恩雷诺茨]]和[[布蕾克·萊芙莉|布莱克莱弗利]]体恤运动。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Ryan Reynolds Recruited Blake Lively's Mom To Sell 'Obscenely Boring Shirts' For COVID-19 Relief|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3163461/ryan-reynolds-coronavirus-charity-shirt/|date=2020-04-17|last=Vincent|first=Brittany|publisher=MTV News|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421161906/http://www.mtv.com/news/3163461/ryan-reynolds-coronavirus-charity-shirt/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[米沙·克林斯|米莎柯林斯]]改期了他为期一周的寻宝活动；GISH（世界上最大的国际寻宝游戏），改成了为期一天的收费居家寻宝游戏，这些注册费会被用来给由于疫情居家隔离所失去食物来源的孩子们。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Misha Collins Talks His Play-at-Home, Mini Gish Scavenger Hunt|url=https://www.themarysue.com/misha-collins-talks-his-mini-gish-scavenger-hunt/|date=2020-04-20|last=Mason|first=Jessica|website=themarysue.com|access-date=2020-04-21|archive-date=2020-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423151938/https://www.themarysue.com/misha-collins-talks-his-mini-gish-scavenger-hunt/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

