== 非盈利组织 ==
由于大流行导致失业率上升，许多提供粮食供给的[[非营利组织|非营利组织]]创建了粮食分配计划，以缓解当地[[食物銀行|粮食银行]]的压力。非盈利性组织（如Feeding America，World Central Kitchen和Half-Table Man Disasters）会致力于将食品直接分发给个人或食品银行。<ref>{{Cite news|last=Giordano|first=Medea|url=https://www.wired.com/story/covid-19-charities-nonprofits-companies-helping/|title=The Nonprofits and Companies Helping to Fight the Pandemic|date=2020-04-18|work=Wired|access-date=2020-04-20|issn=1059-1028|archive-date=2020-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418024324/https://www.wired.com/story/covid-19-charities-nonprofits-companies-helping/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

其他组织，例如[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]，敦促将捐赠的款项交给COVID-19 Solidarity Response Fund，这是一个中央基金，旨在帮助全球范围内的关键应急工作。<ref>{{Cite web|title=COVID-19 Response Fund|url=https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/donate|publisher=World Health Organization|access-date=2020-04-20|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420170225/https://www.who.int/emergencies/diseases/novel-coronavirus-2019/donate|dead-url=no}}</ref>作为一项用于基本药物费和基本生活费的应急基金，The Actors Fund通过在Youtube上现场直播由拉明·卡里姆鲁，塞拉·博格斯和哈德利·弗雷泽主演的电影 《The Phantom of the Opera at London's Royal Albert Hall》来提供娱乐和筹款。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Not Only Should You Stream The Phantom of the Opera This Weekend, You Have To|url=https://www.vulture.com/2020/04/actors-fund-livestreams-phantom-of-the-opera-for-charity.html|date=2020-04-18|last=Kiefer|first=Halle|language=en-us|website=Vulture|access-date=2020-05-09|archive-date=2020-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200424123052/https://www.vulture.com/2020/04/actors-fund-livestreams-phantom-of-the-opera-for-charity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

为了避免对他们关照的动物产生负面影响，全世界的当地动物收容所和救援组织都减少了服务，并在大流行期间惩罚动物的收养或饲养。<ref>{{Cite web|title=How you can help during the coronavirus outbreak|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/03/21/how-you-can-help-during-coronavirus/?arc404=true|date=2020-04-06|last=Vongkiatkajorn|first=Kanyakrit|last2=Daily|first2=Laura|website=The Washington Post|access-date=2020-04-19|archive-date=2020-04-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418230500/https://www.washingtonpost.com/nation/2020/03/21/how-you-can-help-during-coronavirus/?arc404=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>出于社会或健康方面的考虑，庇护所利用减少社区动物来帮助将省出来的宠物食品分发给那些无法为宠物购买食品的人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=York County SPCA starts pantry to help owners feed pets|url=https://www.abc27.com/news/local/york/york-county-spca-starts-pantry-to-help-owners-feed-pets/|date=2020-04-20|last=Pritchett|first=Valerie|website=ABC27|access-date=2020-04-21|archive-date=2020-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200421225726/https://www.abc27.com/news/local/york/york-county-spca-starts-pantry-to-help-owners-feed-pets/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

